{"title":"「Project Euler 9」特殊勾股数","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":256,"tags":["数论","Special Judge"],"operation":{"submit":"https://syzoj.com/problem/1017#submit_code","submissions":"https://syzoj.com/submissions?problem_id=1017","statistics":"https://syzoj.com/problem/1017/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://syzoj.com/problem/1017/testdata","discussion":"https://syzoj.com/discussion/problem/1017"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"一组勾股数由三个自然数组成，$a < b < c$，且\r\n\r\n$$a^2 + b^2 = c^2$$\r\n\r\n例如，$3^2 + 4^2 = 9 + 16 = 25 = 5^2$。\r\n\r\n给出 $N$，请输出所有满足 $a + b + c = N$ 的勾股数。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"只有一行，一个整数 $N$。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"多行，每行三个整数，$a, b, c$，表示答案。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 样例输入 1\r\n```plain\r\n12\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出 1\r\n```plain\r\n3 4 5\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输入 2\r\n```plain\r\n120\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出 2\r\n```plain\r\n30 40 50\r\n20 48 52\r\n24 45 51\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"对于 $20\\%$ 的数据，$N \\leq 5000$。\r\n\r\n对于 $40\\%$ 的数据，$N \\leq 1000000$。\r\n\r\n对于 $100\\%$ 的数据，$N \\leq 10^{12}$。"}]}